Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: 10,842 square foot retail plaza for sale in Woodstock, Ontario. The property is on the prominent corner of Dundas Street and Springbank Avenue. The Tenants include a mix of national franchises and independent retailers. The property is shadow anchored by McDonalds, TD Canada Trust along with a number of high profile retailers.

Busy plaza at the corner of Springbank and Dundas. High traffic area with adjacent tenants including McDonalds, Tim Hortons, TD Bank, Shoppers Drug Mart, Zehrs, and LCBO. Good signage opportunity. Existing tenants include Little Caesars, Dentist, First Choice Hair Cutters. Total available space of 925 sq. ft.

Busy plaza at the corner of Springbank and Dundas. High traffic area with adjacent tenants including McDonalds, Tim Hortons, TD Bank, Shoppers Drug Mart, Zehrs, and LCBO. Good signage opportunity. Existing tenants include Little Caesars, Dentist, First Choice Hair Cutters. Total available space of 925 sq. ft.

BUILD-TO-Suit opportunity in Circle K/Esso plaza adjacent to Sobeys at NW Corner of Devonshire & Springbank. Property has just been re-zoned to allow for automotive service shop such as Oil change/Lube shop, Muffler shop, Transmission shop, Auto Glass, Auto Detailing or any other high profile services. Base Building includes lab-on-grade concrete floor, 3 drive-in overhead doors, 10% office/showroom with lights & ceilings, 1 washroom, unit heaters in warehouse, AC in office, hydro to panel. 10 year term, 2nd 5 years @ $28.00 psf. Additional requirements can be provided as required and amortized into rents over 10 years. See Sales Brochure link for Feature Sheet download with concept site plan.

Rare opportunity to lease a small, highly visible store in a very busy plaza on the north side of Woodstock next to Sobey's. Unit is located 3rd unit east of Mac's - previously occupied by Kumon. Unit is in excellent condition. High traffic location - great visibility. Contact LB for appointment to show, feature sheet, floor plans zoning and permitted uses. Rental fee for pylon sign.
